        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nFYI: This wasn't catched in CI as for role changes we don't run playbook level tests but I did run it manually and result was same as in target env: https://jenkins.onap.org/job/offline-installer-master-review/927/consoleText:\n\n    TASK [docker : Install required packages] **************************************\n    fatal: [infrastructure-server]: FAILED! => {\"msg\": \"'dict object' has no attribute 'RedHat'\"}\n\nSo the advice here is to run play level tests on local dev env manually to check for play level regressions.",
